Nutrition For Life names Barry Loder COO . Nutrition For Life International said Monday Barry Loder was appointed chief operating officer . The company said Loder is also the company ' s vice president and chief financial officer . The company said David Bertrand , the company ' s president and Chief Executive Officer , was also handling the COO responsibilties before Loder was appointed to the job . Nutrition For Life makes and sells nutritional supplements and other consumer products . 
